name: Dev Patel
summary: Dev Patel is a 30-year-old Software Engineer based in Los Angeles, California. He values family, career success, and helping others. His interests include programming, hiking, photography, and cooking. Fluent in English and Hindi, he is a graduate from the University of California and holds moderate political views. As a dedicated Hindu and an INTJ Scorpio, he is looking for a long-term, monogamous relationship. He is a straight man using he/him/his pronouns and identifies as South Asian. He doesn't have children but wants to in the future. He's an active individual who sometimes drinks but doesn't smoke or use marijuana or other drugs. Dev is seeking a straight woman, aged 25-35, who is also active, wants children in the future, and doesn't smoke.
